{"tid":1274930,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"為自己嘅血源感到可恥","createTime":"2019-07-01T17:39:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T11:15:14.000Z","uid":262825,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6ab2e4d23665b0a556ff5a6d2b29ac5b8f79ec52","tid":1274930,"uid":262825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:39:42.000Z","msg":"為自己老豆娶左一個大陸女人感到可恥<br />\n為自己大伯娶左一個大陸女人感到可恥<br />\n為自己呀叔娶左一個大陸女人感到可恥<br />\n為自己嘅家族感到可恥<br />\n<br />\n今日老人家生日 成家人食飯<br />\n喺酒樓 大家睇住cctvb <br />\n聽住班親戚評論年輕人 話啲暴徒又點點點<br />\n我忍唔住笑左出聲 <br />\n同時為自己生於呢一個家族<br />\n感到慚愧<br />\n<br />\n血源從來都是上天注定 <br />\n所以我決定 同將來我唯一可以由自己選擇的另一半<br />\n必定要好好守護自己下一代並教育他們<br />\n讓他們為生於這家庭而驕傲 而勇敢。"},{"pid":"e5f31fe1ef2666e48f3d7357e3526d74a4f89deb","tid":1274930,"uid":215864,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:41:12.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"9ca5b7a62bb3d606005f71fff403f2ff1378bf20","tid":1274930,"uid":215864,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T17:42:53.000Z","msg":"講明啲 啫喺想比鬼仔屌?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e35e592f2c58b30a4ca70e5ba9ccf90ab832d424","tid":1274930,"uid":18552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:48:46.000Z","msg":"我都唔明點解佢地可以講極都唔明"},{"pid":"b17ac3af5b92a4577604628b192be7eab0850389","tid":1274930,"uid":262825,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e35e592f2c58b30a4ca70e5ba9ccf90ab832d424","tid":1274930,"uid":18552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T18:48:46.000Z","msg":"我都唔明點解佢地可以講極都唔明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T23:25:53.000Z","msg":"因為我地唔係同一種人"},{"pid":"d134a1fd30a4642d85e5dd924bc5af5e2a18f741","tid":1274930,"uid":52194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T23:27:26.000Z","msg":"一家人土生土長<br />\n但老豆深紅<br />\n無得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18702f1c27d06b18f73965940b455a5c2a27101b","tid":1274930,"uid":159913,"like":